{"title":"战士的歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":3,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团结打敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建功部机一连邢书元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新同志，来到班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各个同志笑连连。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤鸣给他军装褂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷凯给他衬衣穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新老战士如兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相帮助要当先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你帮我，我帮你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化技术要多练，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练好技术上战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉着勇敢到阵前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多杀敌人多缴枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立功把罪赎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成功部一连王金盛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六月三伏天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋贼众汉奸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到我家园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进门别不讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用绳把我拴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绑到大队部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"押我十七天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逼我当匪军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担任办事员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匪徒真凶狠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢米又抢面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心害人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶罪滔天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮一声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我来解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽大又优待，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对我教育强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上光明路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活乐洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想转变好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参军上战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕过大水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕爬高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立功把罪赎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉贼老蒋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国得解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民得安康。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担架七尺长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建功部李兰亭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担架七尺长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同我上战场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一气跑上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就把伤员抢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伤员放上边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬至我后方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽不是武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战场作用强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除救伤员外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用处也很广。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上房可做梯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡觉可当床。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过河可架桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处把我帮。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}